# 3. Write a Python Program to Convert Decimal to Binary, Octal and Hexadecimal?

decimal = int(input("Enter a decimal number: "))

binary = bin(decimal)
octal = oct(decimal)
hexadecimal = hex(decimal)

print("Binary: ", binary)
print("Octal: ", octal)
print("Hexadecimal: ", hexadecimal)


